#Level 0

Objective: The goal of this level is for you to log into the game using SSH. The host to which you need to connect is bandit.labs.overthewire.org, on port 2220. The username is bandit0 and the password is bandit0. 

Solution: For this task I utilized the command prompt to write down the ssh command needed to connect to OverTheWire's linux server. 
Command is 'ssh bandit0@bandit.labs.overthewire.org -p 2220'
Where: ssh is the protocol, bandit0 is mentioned as the username as given, bandit.labs.overthewire...etc is the domain name and the -p command allows me to connect to the port number listed as 2220, if this were a standard SSH, it would be -p 22 since it uses 22 as the default, but OverTheWire uses 2220 as the norm.
Upon entering the command we'll be asked to register the id as a fingerprint, type 'yes' and then repeat the command again to type in the password which is shown in the objective above
